title.zh: 武汉：血友姐妹会大创项目中期报告评级优秀
title.en: Wuhan: Hemophilia Sisters Project Mid-term Report Rated Excellent

description.zh: 华中科技大学血友姐妹会队伍的大创项目中期报告评级优秀。该项目展示了团队在血友病女性关爱领域的研究进展和学术成果，获得了评审专家的高度认可。
description.en: The mid-term report of the Hemophilia Sisters team's innovation and entrepreneurship project at Huazhong University of Science and Technology was rated excellent. The project demonstrated the team's research progress and academic achievements in the field of hemophilia women's care, receiving high recognition from review experts.
